snippet.title: MotionSports Launch Trailer, November 2010 [Europe]
snippet.description: Here is an exclusive look at the new trailer for MotionSports on the Microsoft Kinect. Get ready to play 6 exciting sports through various challenges and make a name in the world of sports!
